  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要画一个序列图，展示HealthTech EMR Sync模块的核心事务流程。关键点是同步任务执行后，如何通过UnitOfWork来管理HealthTech LabAnalyzer相关的变更。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Core",
        "UnitOfWork",
        "HealthTech_EMR_Sync",
        "HealthTech_LabAnalyzer"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白。所以Core模块先执行一些同步任务，然后创建一个UnitOfWork实例来累积变更？这里的UnitOfWork具体对应哪个业务实体？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Core",
        "UnitOfWork",
        "HealthTech_PatientRecords"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，UnitOfWork绑定的是HealthTech_PatientRecords上下文。同步任务执行完毕后，Core会调用commit，把HealthTech_LabAnalyzer相关的变更持久化。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Core",
        "UnitOfWork",
        "commit",
        "HealthTech_LabAnalyzer",
        "HealthTech_PatientRecords"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我打算在Core自调用那里标注\"Executa tarefas síncronas...\"，然后在Note里说明\"Fim do bloco síncrono\"，这样分界更清晰。接着Core调用Repository的commit方法，你看可以吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Core",
        "ProcessExecutionRepository",
        "commit",
        "Note"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "可以，但Repository的具体名称应该是ProcessExecutionRepository，不是CessExecutionRepository。另外commit调用需要是异步激活，因为后面要展开MongoDB的事务细节。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "ProcessExecutionRepository",
        "commit",
        "MongoDB"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "repair",
      "utterance": "收到，我修正了Repository的名称。现在MongoDB内部有三个操作：更新ProcessInstance、管理ExecutableTasks、插入criticalEvents到event_outbox。这三个都要在事务里完成对吧？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "MongoDB",
        "ProcessInstance",
        "ExecutableTasks",
        "event_outbox",
        "criticalEvents"
      ],
      "is_repair": true
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "没错，这三个操作是原子性的。事务提交成功后，Repository返回给Core，然后Core要触发事件发布。这里有个细节——Publisher是EventPublisher，同样绑定HealthTech_PatientRecords上下文。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Repository",
        "Core",
        "EventPublisher",
        "HealthTech_PatientRecords",
        "publishEvents"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "publishEvents的调用方式我标注为异步激活，返回\"Retorno Imediato\"，因为事件发布应该是非阻塞的。这样整个流程就是：同步任务→UoW累积→提交事务→异步发布事件。结构对吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "publishEvents",
        "Retorno Imediato",
        "Core",
        "Publisher"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 9,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "结构正确。不过我需要确认一下——MongoDB事务的开始和结束标注，你用\"INICIAR TRANSAÇÃO\"和\"COMMIT TRANSAÇÃO\"，保持葡萄牙语原文？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "MongoDB",
        "INICIAR TRANSAÇÃO",
        "COMMIT TRANSAÇÃO"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 10,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "是的，保持原文。另外UoW的创建消息我写成\"new UnitOfWork(HealthTech_LabAnalyzer)\"，累积变更标注为\"Acumula alterações (HealthTech_EMR_Sync)\"，这样上下文清晰。",
